# Smart Expense Tracker
A full-stack expense tracker built using **React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB**.

## Features

* Add income and expenses
* View transaction history
* REST API backend
* MongoDB database
* React frontend dashboard

## Tech Stack

Frontend:

* React
* Axios
* Recharts

Backend:

* Node.js
* Express
* MongoDB
* JWT Authentication

## Installation

### Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/smart-expense-tracker.git

### Backend setup

cd backend
npm install
npm run dev

### Frontend setup

cd frontend
npm install
npm start

## Environment Variables

Create `.env` file in backend:

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection
PORT=5000

